{"title":"我愿化作风帆——献给敬爱的党","authors":["万忆萱"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":9,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿化作风帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给敬爱的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万忆萱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我永远也忘不了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——气势磅礴的长江！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了你一泻千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾呼啸的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大形象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞到暗礁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你溅起千堆雪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经遇险滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你激起万重浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不停歇、永不止步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一浪追过一浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你容不得半点杂质，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淘沙涤石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是沙石，卷入江底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弃污去垢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是草芥，抛向岸旁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那浩淼绵亘的巨流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远通体碧透清亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使是乌云蔽日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也闪着粼粼的波光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你宽厚的胸膛里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出那么洪亮的声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如裂石碎金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿锵在无际的苍穹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酷似千军万马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呐喊在辽远的疆场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使弱者惊心动魄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使强者斗志昂扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是战歌，是鼙鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催得人心发热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迸射出难以估计的力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是由于有了你呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡的峰峦才那么——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭拔、峻伟、青翠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是由于有了你呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸的树木才那么——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓊郁、葱茏、茁壮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是由于有了你呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崖畔的鲜花才那么——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娇美、艳丽、芬芳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——你是生命的摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲般的江……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我永远也忘不了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——奔腾豪迈的长江！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了你源远流长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一浪高过一浪的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗形象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真愿化作风帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变作桅樯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你博大的怀抱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远飞翔！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}